language of the physicians. (O.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisotaforaga","text_ar":"اِسْتَفْرَغَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN maA fiY SaHofatihi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ مَا فِى صَحْفَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a prov., meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exhausted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chose for himself, as his share,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the whole of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what was in his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SHfp","text_ar":"صحفة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large bowl"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SHf","text_ar":"صحف"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b4-  And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astfrg fulaAnN majohuwdahu","text_ar":"استفرغ فُلَانٌ مَجْهُودَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one exhausted his power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exerted it unsparingly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the utmost;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * O, Msb, * K, * TA;)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY ka*aA","text_ar":"فِى كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in such a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}